{"tid":1037371,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"比你排杜Sir最經典電影 你會點排?","createTime":"2019-02-26T01:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T01:52:23.000Z","uid":142523,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"431d29f088057a91cd885c7ab510176b35426fd5","tid":1037371,"uid":142523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:37:36.000Z","msg":"1. 暗戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得傾 <br />\n係我第一套留意杜sir既電影,<br />\n青雲同劉華果種張力, 雖然我唔太認同劉華演技,但呢個角色係抵佢拎金像獎,<br />\n但同時登青雲失望, 要到我要成名先拎到第1次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8z5ZAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8z5ZAU.jpg&h=c1e9a507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 鎗火 <br />\n我相信只有男人先會明白既電影感!! 鏡頭運用,拍攝場地,劇情,節奏各方面拿捏得好好,<br />\n主角鎮宇,秋生,張耀揚,任達華 只要有佢地 成套戲即刻有哂畫面,經典既Bgm到而家都有人翻抄黎用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y9YAaA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y9YAaA.jpg&h=962d523e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 黑社會<br />\n大D哥, 東莞仔, 樂少, Jimmy仔, 飛機, 師爺蘇, 大頭<br />\n每個角色設計都有佢既特質, 有血有肉, 彷彿真係出自係現實世界一樣,<br />\n到ending 大D比樂少隊林果幕 華哥亦都演繹到果種寒到入骨既陰暗面,亦都令到佢個仔種下好深既陰影。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwqtcYS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwqtcYS.png&h=356a4320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.神探<br />\n呢套有睇過既巴打, 我相信可能你會問點解我排呢套咁後?<br />\n但我可以同你講呢套戲我係好後期先睇返, 但睇完我覺得青雲係無得輸,<br />\n而結局亦都有驚喜 (未睇既你一定要睇下,)<br />\n最鍾意酒樓食野果幕, 好深刻..<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1DqZFF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1DqZFF.jpg&h=4ba07b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.放。逐<br />\n鎗火原班人馬插入渣渣輝, 再次演活男人既浪漫 , 豪邁既兄弟情,<br />\n亦都係呢套戲令我對任賢齊開始產生好感! 原來佢都可以幾型 (只要唔出聲)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UubPGUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUubPGUh.jpg&h=aab752e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 嚦咕嚦咕新年財<br />\n賀歲片黎講, 除左周星馳某d戲之外, 呢套係我睇極都唔厭,而且年年都會翻睇一次!<br />\n到而家同屋企人打牌都會間唔中講返d對白, <br />\n&quot;人品好, 牌品自然好&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrSjjG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrSjjG3.jpg&h=46ba4f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 純個人觀感討論"},{"pid":"4f68a39351a5ee5c9ba5f8466eb52fceaaabe3a1","tid":1037371,"uid":35045,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"PTU？"},{"pid":"480213b078fd5981a7ac8cea1cd6b222b867277d","tid":1037371,"uid":34567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"柔道龍虎榜一定係第一"},{"pid":"dda516c861e00fa124129542ecb43b96dd1593bb","tid":1037371,"uid":125612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480213b078fd5981a7ac8cea1cd6b222b867277d","tid":1037371,"uid":34567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"柔道龍虎榜一定係第一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊點解無柔道龍虎榜"},{"pid":"2ff6aff8608e372c983c7984bd291448ab062f9e","tid":1037371,"uid":115347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"鎗火<br />\n暗戰<br />\n黑社會<br />\nPTU<br />\n神探<br />\n大隻佬<br />\n文雀<br />\n審死官<br />\n阿郎的故事<br />\n孤男寡女<br />\n單身男女"},{"pid":"ee668909168a838b1fd785619020e41bcd70f403","tid":1037371,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"神探真係好正"},{"pid":"4a1dc603e968924264359960a4904db5cba2d6b8","tid":1037371,"uid":206762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480213b078fd5981a7ac8cea1cd6b222b867277d","tid":1037371,"uid":34567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"柔道龍虎榜一定係第一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗 唔係話其他差 但柔道龍虎榜係我睇杜sir既戲 感受最深既一套"},{"pid":"7fc8004c3744c588c191e484d52df2308b637d49","tid":1037371,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"全部都好本土<br />\n無人搵佢拍合拍片/大陸片?"},{"pid":"6a321a8de3f7ac325